    "We observe that in both plots, vPIM-rust demonstrates considerably slower execution times with 5.2× overhead on average compared to native.",
    "Conversely, the execution time of vPIM-C is closer to the baseline with an average overhead of 1.4×.We further analyze the effectiveness of the optimization by conducting a driver-centric breakdown, showing how three types of operation (write-to-rank, read-from-rank, and CI) contribute to the total execution time.",
    "We use 60 DPUs and 8MB input file size.",
    "This breakdown identifies latency sources and assesses vPIM 's efficiency in handling each operation type.",
